Story: Test JSON parsing functionality

Given:
  json_data: String = "{\"name\":\"Buy milk\",\"done\":false,\"id\":1}"
  task_name: String = ""
  task_done: Boolean = FALSE
  task_id: Integer = 0

Step 1 → Parse task name
  Because: Extract name from JSON
  Then: task_name becomes PARSE JSON json_data GET "name"
  Effect: Print "Task name: {task_name}"

Step 2 → Parse task done status
  Because: Extract done from JSON
  Then: task_done becomes PARSE JSON json_data GET "done"
  Effect: Print "Task done: {task_done}"

Step 3 → Parse task ID
  Because: Extract id from JSON
  Then: task_id becomes PARSE JSON json_data GET "id"
  Effect: Print "Task ID: {task_id}"

End: Return task_name
